OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,FThe "epic mismanagement" of the Ffos-y-
OL,7,FFran opencast mine saga in Merthyr
OL,8,FTydfil must not happen again to any
OL,9,Fcommunity in Wales, according to a
OL,10,FSenedd committee.
OL,12,FA report by the Climate Change,
OL,13,FEnvironment and Infrastructure
OL,14,FCommittee calls for lessons to be
OL,15,Flearnt in how sites are restored after
OL,16,Fmining permits end.
OL,18,FFfos-y-Fran mine was the last opencast
OL,19,Fmine in Wales and the most high-
OL,20,Fprofile site examined by the committee
OL,21,Fin its report.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/18
