OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,FThe license to extract coal from Ffos-
OL,7,Fy-Fran expired in September 2022 but
OL,8,Fthe mine continued to operate for
OL,9,Fanother 14 months, closing in November
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FWhen it first opened, the company
OL,13,Frunning the mine pledged to fully
OL,14,Frestore the site after it finished
OL,15,Foperations, and the committee heard
OL,16,Fevidence that since 2017 the company
OL,17,Fhas paid out nearly #50million in
OL,18,Fdividends and royalties out of the
OL,19,Fbusiness.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
