OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1723131537
OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,FBut the report has found that with
OL,7,Fcurrent restoration costs estimated at
OL,8,Fbetween #50m to #120m, and despite the
OL,9,Foriginal restoration promises, the
OL,10,Fcompany now claims they are unable to
OL,11,Fafford this, leaving the community
OL,12,Fworried about the future of the site.
OL,14,FAlyson and Chris Austin, who live near
OL,15,FFfos-y-Fran and are long-term
OL,16,Fcampaigners on the issue, said: "The
OL,17,Fwhole process has been awful and the
OL,18,Fcommunication from both the council
OL,19,Fand the mining company has been
OL,20,Fappalling throughout.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
