PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1723131537
OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,F"They will only tell us anything when
OL,7,Fthey're absolutely forced to; the
OL,8,Flocal community seem to be at the
OL,9,Fbottom of their list of priorities.
OL,11,F"We have huge concerns about what the
OL,12,Ffuture holds for Ffos-y-Fran. What
OL,13,Fwe'll be left with is a loose and
OL,14,Fsteep-sided valley with a lake at the
OL,15,Fbottom; easily accessible by anyone,
OL,16,Fand a magnet for children.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
