PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1723131537
OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,F"We feel like we've been hung out to
OL,7,Fdry by our local authority, the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment, and government agencies at
OL,9,Fall levels. The mining company should
OL,10,Fbe keeping to its promise of full
OL,11,Frestoration and the council shouldn't
OL,12,Flet them get away with leaving us with
OL,13,Fdangerous and derelict land.
OL,15,F"This restoration of derelict and
OL,16,Fdangerous land was the only benefit to
OL,17,Fus suffering 17 years of opencast coal
OL,18,Fmining on our doorsteps. It's simply
OL,19,Fnot fair that the community is now
OL,20,Fleft in a worse position than we were
OL,21,Fin before this started."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/18
