OL,6,FThis series of events has led the
OL,7,Fcommittee to call for the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment to use stronger enforcement
OL,9,Fmeasures when planning controls are
OL,10,Fbreached, for example, when mining
OL,11,Fcontinued at the site after the
OL,12,Flicence expiration.
OL,14,FThe Senedd committee is also urging
OL,15,Fmore transparency in all aspects of
OL,16,Fthe mining process so the public is
OL,17,Faware of how plans develop.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/18
