OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,FIt calls on the Welsh Government to
OL,7,Frequire local authorities to ensure
OL,8,Fthat all planning reports and
OL,9,Frestoration plans are available online
OL,10,Fand available to the public.
OL,12,FIt also argues that the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment should encourage the use of
OL,14,Fcitizens' assemblies as forums for
OL,15,Fdiscussing the future of restoration
OL,16,Fsites, especially in cases where
OL,17,Frestoration has failed to meet the
OL,18,Foriginal plan and compromises may be
OL,19,Fnecessary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/18
