OL,6,FMerthyr (South Wales) Ltd, the firm
OL,7,Fwhich operated Ffos-y-Fran, issued a
OL,8,Fstatement in May when invited to
OL,9,Fappear before the committee, saying an
OL,10,Finterim restoration programme of works
OL,11,Ffor the site was due to begin in early
OL,12,FMay following agreement with the
OL,13,Fcouncil.
