OL,6,FThe statement said: "MSW have engaged
OL,7,Fthe services of several external
OL,8,Fconsultants, specialists in their
OL,9,Ffield, to prepare a revised
OL,10,Frestoration plan. MSW continues to
OL,11,Fdiscuss with MTCBC and all relevant
OL,12,Fkey stakeholders progress on the
OL,13,Frevised restoration plan.
OL,15,F"Therefore, it would be inappropriate
OL,16,Fto comment further until the revised
OL,17,Frestoration plan has been finalised
OL,18,Fand submitted to MTCBC for their
OL,19,Fconsideration."
