OL,6,FThe firm said a care and maintenance
OL,7,Fteam routinely monitor all safety and
OL,8,Fenvironmental aspects of the site, and
OL,9,Fcomplete daily checks of the water
OL,10,Fquality as well as a quarterly water
OL,11,Ftesting programme agreed with Natural
OL,12,FResources Wales.
OL,14,FIt said water samples are tested by
OL,15,F"an accredited laboratory for a
OL,16,Fcomprehensive suite of determinants.
OL,17,FResults indicate there are no
OL,18,Fdeterminants that raise a cause for
OL,19,Fconcern to the water environment".
