OL,6,FThe committee's report also explores
OL,7,Fthe controversial issue of coal tip
OL,8,Freclamation and who should pay for
OL,9,Fsecuring the safety of more than 2,000
OL,10,Fcoal tips which blight many
OL,11,Fcommunities across Wales.
OL,13,FWhile the UK Government has provided
OL,14,Fsome extra funding in the last few
OL,15,Fyears to mitigate the risk from nearly
OL,16,F300 high-risk tips, as the matter is
OL,17,Fdevolved, they say that the issue
OL,18,Fshould primarily be dealt with by the
OL,19,FWelsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/18
