OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,FHowever, many Welsh politicians have
OL,7,Fargued that, as coal tips are a legacy
OL,8,Fof the country's industrial history
OL,9,Fwhich predates devolution, the UK
OL,10,FGovernment should bear the costs of
OL,11,Fthe longer-term work to make coal tips
OL,12,Fsafe.
OL,14,FThe committee's report urges the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment to engage with the UK
OL,16,FGovernment to seek funding for coal
OL,17,Ftip remediation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/18
