OL,6,FLlyr Gruffydd MS, chair of the Climate
OL,7,FChange, Environment and Infrastructure
OL,8,FCommittee, said, "This report details
OL,9,Fsome of the most egregious examples of
OL,10,Fthe broken promises made to
OL,11,Fcommunities across Wales.
OL,13,F"There has been an epic mismanagement
OL,14,Fof these mines, by all parties, from
OL,15,Fstart to finish.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
