OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1723131537
OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,F"Mining companies have racked up
OL,7,Fenormous profits but when it's time to
OL,8,Ffulfil their restoration promises, the
OL,9,Fwallet is empty. They do as they
OL,10,Fplease and local communities foot the
OL,11,Fbill.
OL,13,F"This is why it's so important for
OL,14,Fcommunity ownership to be considered
OL,15,Fin any new development, which could
OL,16,Flead to more responsible management of
OL,17,Fmining sites.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/18
