OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1723131537
OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,F"Residents told us they felt they had
OL,7,Fbeen completely failed by the public
OL,8,Fauthorities who are meant to protect
OL,9,Fthem. Too often they have seemed to be
OL,10,Fon the side of the mining companies.
OL,12,F"Transparency has been a real problem
OL,13,Fwith residents struggling to get
OL,14,Fanswers from their councils when they
OL,15,Fhave asked legitimate questions about
OL,16,Fmining near their homes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/18
