OL,3,C'Epic mismanagement' of opencast mine
OL,4,Csaga 'must not happen again'
OL,6,F"Time is quickly running out to secure
OL,7,Fwhat was promised for the local
OL,8,Fcommunity in Ffos-y-Fran. We urge the
OL,9,FWelsh Government, Merthyr Tydfil
OL,10,FCounty Borough Council, and other
OL,11,Flocal authorities, to learn the
OL,12,Flessons from this report, so these
OL,13,Fmistakes are never repeated in
OL,14,Fopencast mines or coal tip
OL,15,Freclamations."
