OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says it is
OL,7,F"closely monitoring" the situation at
OL,8,FFfos-y-Fran, while it has committed to
OL,9,Fintroducing new legislation this
OL,10,FSenedd term to deal with the legacy of
OL,11,Fcenturies of mining and to ensure coal
OL,12,Ftip safety for Wales.
OL,14,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We thank the committee for their work
OL,16,Fover the past several months and their
OL,17,Freport. We will consider the report's
OL,18,Ffindings and recommendations and
OL,19,Frespond in due course."
