OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil Council said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "It is pleasing to note
OL,8,Fthat the Climate Change, Environment &
OL,9,FInfrastructure committee commend the
OL,10,Fcouncil for responding positively and
OL,11,Fconstructively to the inquiry and the
OL,12,Frecommendations for Merthyr Tydfil
OL,13,FCounty Borough Council are noted.
OL,15,F"These recommendations reflect the
OL,16,Frequirements of planning legislation
OL,17,Fthat are carried out as part of the
OL,18,Fprocedure of determining planning
OL,19,Fapplications."
